---
title: Balsamic-Cranberry Pork Tenderloin with Mixed Potato Mash and Buttery Veggies
description: Comfort and flavour come to your life with this dinner-time meal. Buttery mixed potato mash and pan-sauteed veggies serve as the bed for a cranberry and balsamic glazed pork tenderloin, proving that wholesome and delicious doesn't have to be complicated!

